data.description: Welcome to this spacious two-story brick-faced Colonial style home available in Lake Olympia.  As you enter the home, a two-story foyer greets you with plenty of light and guides you into the dramatic two-story family room. This bright home has a large Master bedroom downstairs and a split floor plan upstairs with 3 bedrooms and a bonus area that overlooks the downstairs family room and stately wood-burning fireplace. The main floor has a separate dining room and an additional room that can be used as a formal sitting room or as a den/office space. Beautiful wainscoting can be found throughout the house. An additional living space to enjoy is the enclosed lanai directly off the large kitchen. This room allows a full view and access to the backyard through French doors and is large enough to host friend and family gatherings or to serve as a quiet place to relax. Downtown Ocoee is a quick drive. Close to shopping, downtown Winter Garden, the Florida Turnpike, 408, and the 429 with great road access to anywhere in Orlando.
